pageProduct.name: Thompson's Men's Multi 60 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Thompson's Men's Multi 60 tabs One-A-Day multivitamin and mineral complex with antioxidants to support an active lifestyle

Thompson's Men's Multi 60 tabs hHelps provide antioxidants for the maintenance of good health. Helps to support energy production and is beneficial during times of stress. Aids to maintain or improve general wellbeing

Size: 60tabs

Gender: Male

Alcohol Free?: n/a

KEY FEATURES

• Helps provide antioxidants for the maintenance of good health.
• Helps to support energy production and is beneficial during times of stress.
• Aids to maintain or improve general wellbeing.

Warnings

The recommended daily amount of Vitamin A from all sources is 900mcg retinol equivalents (RE) for men. This product contains Selenium which is toxic in high doses. A daily dose of 150mcg for adults of Selenium from dietary supplements should not be exceeded. Vitamin and mineral supplements should not replace a balanced diet. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional.

CAUTION

Do not use if bottle and/or cap seal is missing or broken. Keep out of reach of children.

Ingredients

Active Ingredients: Each tablet contains:
Ascorbic Acid (Vit. C) 206.5mg
Biotin 50mcg
Calcium (as Calcium citrate tetrahydrate) 10.5mg
Calcium pantothenate 100mg
equiv. Pantothenic acid (Vit. B5) 90mg
Choline bitartrate 30mg
Chromium (as Chromium picolinate) 10mcg
Citrus bioflavonoids extract 30mg
Colecalciferol 5mcg
equiv. Vit. D3 200IU
Copper (as Copper gluconate) 600mcg
Cyanocobalamin (Vit. B12) 50mcg
d-alpha-tocopheryl acid succinate 82.6mg
equiv. Vit. E 100IU
Folic acid 90mcg
Fucus vesiculosus (Kelp) ext. 5mg
derived from dry whole plant 25mg
equiv. Iodine 5mcg
Inositol 30mg
Magnesium (as Magnesium amino acid chelate) 10mg
Manganese (as Manganese amino acid chelate) 700mcg
Medicago sativa (Alfalfa) herb powder 5mg
Nicotinamide (Vit. B3) 50mg
Panax ginseng (Korean Ginseng) ext. 20mg
derived from dry root 200mg
Pyridoxine hydrochloride 25mg
equiv. Pyridoxine (Vit. B6) 20.6mg
Retinyl acetate 354mcg
equiv. Vit. A 300mcg RE
Riboflavine (Vit. B2) 30mg
Selenium (as Selenomethionine) 26mcg
Thiamine hydrochloride (Vit. B1) 30mg
Vitis vinifera (Grape) 1mg
derived from dry seed 120mg
std. to contain Procyanidins 950mcg
Zinc (as Zinc amino acid chelate) 15mg

Directions

Store below 30°C in a dry place.

Storage Temperature: Below 30°C

RECYCLABLE INFORMATION

Remove cap. Recycle glass bottle.

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
